---
import Github from '../assets/icons-vectors/github.svg?url';
import Linkedin from '../assets/icons-vectors/linkedin.svg?url';
import Twitter from '../assets/icons-vectors/twitter.svg?url';
---

<section id="contact" class="h-180 p-4 mt-5">
  <h1 class="uppercase text-5xl text-center">Let's work together</h1>
  <p class="mt-3">
    Looking for a global developer to join your team or build your next app? I'm
    currently open to new opportunities in mobile development and beyond.
    Whether you have a project idea, a role to discuss, or just want to connect
    — let's talk.
  </p>
  <div
    class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-between p-2 lg:w-2/5 mx-auto my-4"
  >
    <button class="border-2 border-white rounded-sm p-3 lg:w-2/5">Say Hi</button
    >
    <button class="border-2 border-white rounded-sm p-3 lg:w-2/5"
      >Book a Call</button
    >
  </div>
  <h4 class="uppercase text-center">or</h4>
  <div class="flex justify-between lg:w-1/3 lg:mx-auto mt-3">
    <div class="flex-col">
      <img src={Github} alt="icon" class="w-10 h-auto" />
      <span>Github</span>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-col">
      <img src={Linkedin} alt="icon" class="w-10 h-auto" />
      <span>Linkedin</span>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-col">
      <img src={Twitter} alt="icon" class="w-10 h-auto" />
      <span>Twitter</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
